The paper discusses the use of Doc2Vec algorithm to generate related articles in PubMed, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. This suggests that the paper may belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), or Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
